// (3) amount: Chooses which direction and how much to shift. 
//     (a) 2'b00: shift left by 1 bit. 
//     (b) 2'b01: shift left by 8 bits. 
//     (c) 2'b10: shift right by 1 bit. 
//     (d) 2'b11: shift right by 8 bits. 
// (4) q: The contents of the shifter..
